PortSystem      1.0

name            cfourcc
version	        0.1.2
categories      multimedia
maintainers     avc-cvut.cz:petr.vacek
description     change avi fourcc codes
long_description \
                Command-line utility for changing FOURCC codes in AVI files
homepage        http://sarovar.org/projects/gfourcc/
platforms       darwin
